snippet.title: Good Robot Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Good Robot on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/358...
For more info, please visit http://pyrodactyl.com/

It's 2031. Humanity made robots to do all the boring jobs. It left humans to do exciting things, like fighting all the malfunctioning robots.

But now that's your job. You're a Good Robot, and it's your mission to protect all the human beings on the colony.

There's got to be a few around somewhere...
